    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Decorative bar-shaped devices with a clasp designed to hold the hair in place, particularly such devices to hold long hair pulled to the back of the neck or a section of hair pulled to the top of the head, away from the face.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
